cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.PL

The paper deals with model checking of strategic abilities, which involves logical reasoning and game theory concepts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also proposes translations of formulae, which involves artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also deals with game theory concepts, making cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) a likely category. The paper involves fixpoint expressions, which are related to data structures, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with logical specifications, making cs.PL (Programming Languages) a possible category.
